BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 1 (KCNA) -- The Indian paper INDIAN 
TIMES carried the full text of "For the Ultimate Solution of the 
Rural Question Under the Banner of the Socialist Rural Theses", 
a letter sent by the great leader President Kim Il-song to a 
national agricultural conference. 
  Detailed gists of the letter were carried by the Cameroonian 
paper LA VISION and the Bulgarian paper TRIBUNA. 
  The Togolese paper ATOPANI and the Zairean paper LE STANDARD 
carried articles explaining his work "10-point Programme of the 
Great Unity of the Whole Nation for the Reunification of the 
Country". 

